name: IBI Group Inc. 6.50% Listed Senior Unsecured Debentures due December 31 2025
longDescription: IBI Group Inc. is a global design and technology company. The Company offers a range of services, including architectural controls, architecture, bridge engineering, civil engineering, construction management, data analytics, design technology, development engineering, economics/financial analysis, electrical engineering, energy solutions, engineering, environmental assessment, geomatics/land surveying, highway and road design, and indigenous engagement and relations. The Company's services also include interiors, land use planning, landscape architecture, mechanical engineering, municipal infrastructure, operations and maintenance, parametric design, placemaking, planning and urban design, public outreach, research and development, software development, systems engineering, traffic engineering, transit planning, transportation engineering, visualization, water resources management, and water/wastewater. The Company has over 60 offices in major urban centers across the globe.
